            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH7x2046-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:07:18.26+09:00">East of the Milky Way</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:07:44.01+09:00">there was a weaving girl,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:08:04.213+09:00">who was the daughter of the Sovereign of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:08:38.032+09:00">Year in and Year out she toiled away at weaving cloth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:09:34.138+09:00">and she finished weaving the cloud-brocade Garment of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:10:04.908+09:00">Her own appearance she had not the time to pay proper attention to.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:12:13.481+09:00">The Sovereign of Heaven felt sorry for here living all alone</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:13:21.624+09:00">and he allowed her to get married to a buffalo shepherd from East of the Milky Way.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:13:57.838+09:00">After she got parried she then gave up weaving,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:14:20.443+09:00">and the Sovereign of Heaven got angry at her.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T04:07:38.563+09:00">                                    He gave her an official order to return to Milky Way East,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2046_CHANT_002-135a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T00:18:19.331+09:00">and he only let them meet once per year.</seg>
                </p>
